article.description: — Hunter McIntosh had 21 points as Elon beat Northeastern 67-54 on Saturday.
article.headline: McIntosh scores 21 to carry Elon past Northeastern 67-54
article.linkText: McIntosh scores 21 to carry Elon past Northeastern 67-54
article.story: BOSTON -- — Hunter McIntosh had 21 points as Elon beat Northeastern 67-54 on Saturday. Darius Burford had 15 points for Elon (10-21, 7-11 Colonial Athletic Association). Michael Graham added 10 points and 10 rebounds. Zac Ervin had eight rebounds. Jason Strong had 14 points for the Huskies (8-21, 2-16). Jahmyl Telfort added 13 points. Nikola Djogo had eight rebounds. The Phoenix improve to 2-0 against the Huskies this season. Elon defeated Northeastern 79-62 on Dec. 29. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
